cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper deals with affect recognition in ads using multimodal features, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. cs.MM (Multimedia) is the most likely category as the paper deals with audio-visual features. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses convolutional neural networks for feature extraction. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are possible categories as the paper deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. Finally, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for affect recognition.
